mil.nga.giat.geowave.mapreduce

Class JobContextIndexStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • mil.nga.giat.geowave.mapreduce.JobContextIndexStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IndexStore

    public class JobContextIndexStore
extends Object
implements IndexStore
    This class implements an index store by first checking the job context for an index and keeping a local cache of indices that have been discovered. It will check the metadata store if it cannot find an index in the job context.
